wivrn (0.22-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Passthrough streaming support
  * Fully encrypted connection
  * Improved compositor pacing
  * Add wivrnctl utility to control server

 -- Patrick Nicolas <patricknicolas@laposte.net>  Thu, 05 Dec 2024 22:20:41 +0100

wivrn (0.21-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fixed multiple dashboard issues
    - Missing tray icon
    - Uncaught exception if the model property is not set on the android device
    - Uncaught exception if the Steam app manifest does not exist
    - Assertion failure when the settings window is opened a second time
    - Avoid double error message if the server fails to start
    - Correctly set the app id for non-Steam games that are added in the Steam library
  * Improved compositor pacing
  * Changed default encoder configuration
  * Inhibit sleeping while a session is active
  * Avahi publication is now optional
  * Always set the active runtime even if there was already one

 -- Guillaume Meunier <guillaume.meunier@centraliens.net>  Sun, 03 Nov 2024 14:35:12 +0100

